All code is written, integrated, and ready to use. Just follow the setup steps above and you're good to go! 🚀**Status: ✨ Ready to Deploy**---- [ ] Performance optimized- [ ] Analytics integrated- [ ] User testing completed- [ ] University data connects to real database- [ ] Real RIASEC filtering enabled🎉 **Ready for Production** when:- [ ] No console errors- [ ] Responsive design works on all devices- [ ] My Matches shows exact saved count- [ ] Choices persist across page refreshes- [ ] Users can swipe through all universities- [ ] All 100 universities seed successfully✅ **Feature Complete** when:## Success Metrics---```└── UNIVERSITY_DISCOVERY_SETUP.md (250 lines) ⭐ NEW├── .env.example (UPDATED)├── seed.js (290 lines) ⭐ NEWroot/└── pathfinder.css (unchanged)├── index.css (unchanged)├── App.jsx (UPDATED +2 routes)│   └── SwipeButtons.jsx (35 lines) ⭐ NEW│   ├── UniversityCard.jsx (70 lines) ⭐ NEW├── components/│   └── Nav.jsx (UPDATED +2 links)│   ├── MyMatchesPage.jsx (190 lines) ⭐ NEW│   ├── DiscoverPage.jsx (310 lines) ⭐ NEW├── pages/src/```**Complete file listing with line counts:**## Files Reference---→ Ensure AuthContext is provided at App root level### AuthContext not working→ Clear cache, verify pathfinder.css in index.css import chain### CSS looks broken→ Verify RLS policy allows `auth.uid() = user_id`### Choices not saving→ Check Supabase connection, RLS policies, and seed completion### Error: "Failed to load universities"## Troubleshooting---8. **Save as PDF** - Export shortlist7. **University Reviews** - Add student testimonials/ratings6. **Advanced Filters** - By location, tuition, selectivity5. **Share Shortlist** - Email or share with friends/counselor4. **Comparison Feature** - Pick 2-3 and compare side-by-side3. **University Details Modal** - Click card to see more info2. **Real RIASEC Filtering** - Connect assessment results to filter universities1. **Add University Images** - Upload logos/photos to Supabase Storage## Next Steps (Optional Enhancements)---- [ ] Mobile responsive layout works- [ ] Refresh page; previous choices persist- [ ] Empty state in My Matches works- [ ] Dashboard shows updated match count- [ ] Can remove a match- [ ] My Matches shows all saved universities- [ ] "See My Matches" button works- [ ] Completion screen shows after last card- [ ] Progress bar updates correctly- [ ] Arrow keys work (← = No, → = Yes)- [ ] Swipe right (Yes) moves to next card and saves- [ ] Swipe left (No) moves to next card- [ ] Can click Discover and see first university- [ ] Nav shows "Discover" and "My Matches" links- [ ] `seed.js` ran without errors- [ ] Database tables created successfully## Testing Checklist---| Blue | Purple | Pink | Green | Orange | Gray ||---|---|---|---|---|---|| R | I | A | S | E | C |### RIASEC Badge Colors- **Body:** DM Sans (sans-serif, 400/500/600)- **Headings:** Playfair Display (serif, 900)### Fonts- **Background:** `var(--bg)` #f9fafb- **Secondary:** `var(--green)` #2d6a4f- **Accent:** `var(--teal-pale)` #ccfbf1- **Hover:** `var(--teal-light)` #14b8a6- **Primary:** `var(--teal)` #0d9488### Colors Used## Styling System---```<MyMatchesPage setActivePage={setActivePage} />```jsx### MyMatchesPage```<DiscoverPage setActivePage={setActivePage} />```jsx### DiscoverPage```/>  disabled={false}  onYes={() => handleYes()}  onNo={() => handleNo()}<SwipeButtons ```jsx### SwipeButtons```/>  isVisible={true}  university={{id, name, city, type, riasec_tags, description}}<UniversityCard ```jsx### UniversityCard## Component API Reference---Once RIASEC assessment data is stored, this can be enabled.```  .overlaps('riasec_tags', userTopTraits); // e.g. ["I", "A", "E"]  .select('*')  .from('universities')const { data: filtered } = await supabase```javascriptCurrently shows **all 100 universities**. To filter by RIASEC:### 🔄 Filtering Logic (For Future)6. **Keyboard Support** - Arrow keys for power users5. **Responsive Grid** - Works great on mobile, tablet, desktop4. **Real-time Saving** - No "submit" button needed; choice saved immediately3. **Skip Already-Decided** - Prevents showing cards user already swiped2. **UPSERT with onConflict** - Handles re-swiping the same university1. **Supabase RLS Policies** - Data privacy: each user only sees/modifies their own choices### ✅ Why This Approach## Key Technical Decisions---```    └─ [Back to Dashboard]    ├─ Remove button on each    ├─ Grid of all "yes" universitiesMy Matches Page (MyMatchesPage.jsx)        ↓    [See My Matches →]    Completion Screen        ↓    [After all universities reviewed]        ↓    └─ [Saves to Supabase instantly]    ├─ [Arrow keys work too]    ├─ Swipe: ✕ No / ✓ Yes    │  └─ Description    │  ├─ RIASEC badges (color-coded)    │  ├─ Name, City, Type    ├─ University Card with:    ├─ See Progress: "1 of 100"Discover Page (DiscoverPage.jsx)    ↓[Click "Discover Universities" CTA]    ↓Dashboard```## User Experience Flow---5. Verify choices saved in Supabase dashboard4. Check `/my-matches` to see saved ones3. Swipe through universities2. Navigate to `/discover` (via navbar or dashboard CTA)1. Start dev server: `npm run dev`### 4️⃣ Test the Feature**Output:** Should see ✅ Seeded 100 universities!```node seed.js```bash### 3️⃣ Seed the DatabaseGet this from Supabase → Settings → API```SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=your-service-role-key```Add to `.env`:### 2️⃣ Configure Environment Variables```  FOR SELECT USING (true);CREATE POLICY "Public read universities" ON universitiesALTER TABLE universities ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;  FOR ALL USING (auth.uid() = user_id);CREATE POLICY "Users manage own choices" ON user_university_choicesALTER TABLE user_university_choices ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;);  UNIQUE(user_id, university_id)  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(),  choice TEXT CHECK (choice IN ('yes', 'no')),  university_id INT REFERENCES universities(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,  user_id UUID REFERENCES auth.users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,  id UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() PRIMARY KEY,CREATE TABLE user_university_choices (CREATE INDEX idx_universities_riasec_tags ON universities USING GIN (riasec_tags););  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()  description TEXT,  riasec_tags TEXT[],  type TEXT,  city TEXT,  name TEXT NOT NULL,  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,CREATE TABLE universities (```sqlRun in Supabase SQL Editor:### 1️⃣ Create Database Tables (SQL)## Setup Steps---With Row Level Security enabled for data privacy.```UNIQUE(user_id, university_id)created_at (TIMESTAMPTZ)choice (TEXT) - 'yes' or 'no'university_id (INT FK → universities)user_id (UUID FK → auth.users)id (UUID PRIMARY KEY)```### user_university_choices```created_at (TIMESTAMPTZ)description (TEXT)riasec_tags (TEXT[]) - Array of R, I, A, S, E, or Ctype (TEXT) - Public, Private, Technical, Medicine, Arts, Military, Researchcity (TEXT)name (TEXT)id (SERIAL PRIMARY KEY)```### universities (100 rows included)## Database Schema---| `.env.example` | Added SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY variable || `src/pages/DashboardPage.jsx` | Added CTA banner + stat tracking || `src/pages/Nav.jsx` | Added 2 new navigation links || `src/App.jsx` | Added routes for Discover & MyMatches pages ||------|---------|| File | Changes |### Files Updated| `UNIVERSITY_DISCOVERY_SETUP.md` | Comprehensive setup guide || `src/components/SwipeButtons.jsx` | Yes/No button component (35 lines) || `src/components/UniversityCard.jsx` | Reusable card component (70 lines) || `src/pages/MyMatchesPage.jsx` | Matches grid view (190 lines) || `src/pages/DiscoverPage.jsx` | Main swipe interface (310 lines) || `seed.js` | Seeds 100 Romanian universities into Supabase ||------|---------|| File | Purpose |### Files Created   - Full integration with existing state-based routing   - Added "My Matches" link in navbar   - Added "Discover" link in navbar4. **Navigation**   - One-click access from dashboard   - Stat showing number of saved universities   - New gradient CTA banner to "Discover Universities"3. **Dashboard Integration**   - Match count tracking   - Empty state with call-t